.BR attributes (5)
.SH DIAGNOSTICS
.sp
.LP
\fBpwconv\fR exits with one of the following values:
.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 0
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
.B SUCCESS.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 1
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Permission denied.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 2
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Invalid command syntax.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 3
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Unexpected failure.  Conversion not done.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 4
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Unexpected failure.  Password file(s) missing.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 5
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Password file(s) busy.  Try again later.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B 6
.ad
.RS 5n
.rt
Bad entry in
.B /etc/shadow
file.
.RE

